(1, 'Moroccanoil', 'Leaders in oil-infused beauty, MOROCCANOIL has grown to global success. With its nourishing Argan Oil formulas and signature scent, it\'s easy to see why this brand has cult status amongst its fans.'),
(2, 'Olaplex', 'The original bond builder, OLAPLEX revolutionised professional colour services with its innovative hair rebuilding system. For professional salon use and ongoing at-home maintenance, hair is healthier, stronger and colour is brighter.'),
(3, 'Philip Kingsley', 'With foundations in Trichotherapy, Philip Kingsley solves hair and scalp concerns from the inside out with high quality formulas that encourage healthy hair growth and increased volume.'),
(4, 'Evo', 'born from a desire to shake up the hair industry status quo, we have grown from an aussie upstart into a global movement of salons, stylists and free thinkers. from humble beginnings to big ideas… our mission has remained the same: saving ordinary humans from themselves.'),
(5, '360', 'Gentle on hair and its environment, 360 Color is a collection of cruelty, paraben and gluten free permanent hair colour creams. Designed for busy salons, 360 Color is a high performing range with an economical price tag.'),
(6, 'Lakme', 'Created by stylists, the Lakmé hair collection is committed to innovation and sustainability. With its Mediterranean origins, traditional values and beauty have inspired Lakmé salon colours, tools and products.'),
(7, 'Teknia Organic', 'Created by stylists, the Lakmé hair collection is committed to innovation and sustainability. With its Mediterranean origins, traditional values and beauty have inspired Lakmé salon colours, tools and products.'),
(8, 'Wella', 'Celebrating 140 years of hair passion, Wella delivers innovations and services that empower salon professionals to achieve new creative heights. Founded in 1880 by Franz Stoher in Germany, Wella specialises in hair care and professional hair colour ranges designed for optimal performance. From Koleston Perfect Permanent Hair Colour to Colour Touch Demi-Permanent Hair Colour, Wella has a range of colouring options to suit any client. For cool blondes, shop Blondor cream and powder lighteners.'),
(9, 'Keune', 'With a passion for hair, luxury and high quality ingredients, the Keune range of colour, care, styling and grooming products are designed for all hair types, so you can create looks you client will love.'),
(10, 'Babyliss Pro', ''),
(11, 'Silver Bullet', ''),
(12, 'K.Therapy', 'Created by stylists, the Lakmé hair collection is committed to innovation and sustainability. With its Mediterranean origins, traditional values and beauty have inspired Lakmé salon colours, tools and products.'),
(13, 'Reuzel', 'Believed to be the world\'s finest male grooming products, Reuzel\'s range of pomades, shaving tonics and skin care are influenced by the rock \'n roll, kustom culture and the working class ethnic of Rotterdam.'),
(14, 'Fusion', 'Fusion caters to a wide variety of haircare services. From styling tools, foils, safety equipment and sundries, Fusion has all you need for a busy salon.'),
(15, 'CLOUD NINE Alchemy', 'CLOUD NINE Irons, Wands and Hairdryers set the standard for professional styling with two exclusive collections Sericite and Alchemy. One for you, one for your clients. CLOUD NINE are transforming their collaboration with the haircare industry; in salons with Sericite and at home with Alchemy. Kinder to you. Kinder to your clients. Kinder to everyone.'),
(16, 'CLOUD NINE Sericite', 'CLOUD NINE Irons, Wands and Hairdryers set the standard for professional styling with two exclusive collections Sericite and Alchemy. One for you, one for your clients. CLOUD NINE are transforming their collaboration with the haircare industry; in salons with Sericite and at home with Alchemy. Kinder to you. Kinder to your clients. Kinder to everyone.'),
(17, 'Wahl', 'A household name in haircare, Wahl professional grooming products have been cutting and styling hair since 1919. With quality clippers, trimmers and more, it\'s easy to see why barbers and stylists choose Wahl.'),
