(15, 'pure-blonde-silver-daily-conditioner', 'Pure Blonde Silver Daily Conditioner', 'A purple toning conditioner to reduce yellow discolouration and brassiness in blonde, grey hair. Dramatically enhance the glossiness of blondes with Pure Blonde Silver Daily Conditioner by Philip Kingsley.', '<ul><li>Purple toning conditioner formulated for blonde or dull grey hair</li><li>Optical Brighteners and Violet Hues reduce yellow discolouration and brassiness</li><li>Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein helps strengthen and moisturise </li><li>Fluoresces under UV light, making hair appear brighter and healthier</li><li>Makes highlights stay fresher for longer between salon visits</li><li>Features a calming and soothing lavender fragrance</li><li>Won\'t stain hair like other violet conditioner, making it suitable for daily use</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $44.00.</p><p>Philip Kingsley Pure Blonde Silver Daily Conditioner is formulated with Optical Brighteners and Violet Hues to reduce yellow discolouration and brassiness in blondes and dull greys. This purple toning conditioner reflects under UV light, helping blondes to look brighter, healthier, shinier and glossier. Added Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein helps to strengthen, while its cationic properties enhance shine and moisture retention. This conditioner is perfect for blondes who struggle to achieve shine, or experience dryness due to regular highlights. Pure Blonde Silver Daily Conditioner will keep blondes looking fresh between salon visits.<br/></p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Wheat Protein</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua/Water/Eau, Cetearyl Alcohol, Dimethicone, Behentrimonium Chloride, Silicone Quaternium-18, Hydroxypropyltrimonium Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Trideceth-6, Trideceth-12, Disodium Distyrylbiphenyl Disulfonate, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Oil, Ethylhexylglycerin, lsopropyl Alcohol, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum (Fragrance), Linalool, Benzyl Salicylate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Cl 60730 (Ext .Violet 2).                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>After shampooing with Pure Blonde Silver Shampoo, gently work Pure Blonde Silver Conditioner into the hair, particularly mid-lengths and ends.</li><li>Leave in for 3 minutes to intensify the effect.</li><li>Rinse well and follow with the appropriate Philip Kingsley Scalp Toner.</li><li>Use in combination with Swimcap during summer or when swimming to prevent discolouration.</li></ol></div>', '82088_thumbnail_3.png', 3, 3, 2, '82088', 47, 63, 0.432264, 15, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(16, 'bride-of-gluttony-volumising-conditioner', 'Bride of Gluttony Volumising Conditioner', 'A light-weight volumising conditioner to thicken fine hair. Build body and style support with Bride of Gluttony Volumising Conditioner by Evo.', '<ul><li>Volume-boosting conditioner that minimises frizz and protects from UV damage</li><li>Hydrolyzed Quinoa strengthens and protects while retaining colour vibrancy</li><li>Polyquaternium-10 and 11 thicken and add style support</li><li>Floral, citrus, blackcurrant, fruity and green fragrance notes</li><li>Vegan and cruelty free</li><li>Made without sulphates, parabens or gluten</li><li>Recommended for fine, flat, limp hair</li></ul><p>Evo Gluttony Volumising Shampoo gives fine, limp hair a well-deserved body boost without weighing it down. This volumising conditioner incorporates Hydrolyzed Quinoa to strengthen and protect the hair fibre, helping to retain colour and promote vibrancy. Added Polyquaternium-10 and 11 increase the hair\'s volume while adding style support with anti-static properties. Benzophonene-4 protects the hair from ultraviolet light so its texture and shine maintain integrity. Bride of Gluttony increases the hair\'s softness and smoothness without compromising its thickness. This vegan shampoo features floral, citrus, blackcurrant, fruity and green fragrance notes. Use in conjunction with Gluttony Volumising Shampoo for optimal results.<br/></p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Benzophenone-4</li><li>Anti-Static Agent</li><li>Anti-Static Agent</li><li>Quinoa</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua, Cetyl Alcohol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Isopropyl Myristate, Glyceryl Stearate, Polyquaternium-10, Cetrimonium Chloride, Ceteareth-20, Parfum, Phenoxyethanol, Amodimethicone, Polyquaternium-11, Panthenol, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Hydrolyzed Quinoa, Lactic Acid, Benzoic Acid, Dehydroacetic Acid, Tride