(18, 'extra-volume-conditioner', 'Extra Volume Conditioner', 'A weightless conditioner to nourish and add volume to fine, limp hair. Transform and volumise hair from lifeless to lively with Extra Volume Conditioner by MOROCCANOIL.', '<ul><li>Argan Oil infused conditioner to deeply nourish and detangle</li><li>Glycerin and Cocamide MEA moisturise, soften and boost shine</li><li>Tilia Tomentosa Bud Extract naturally plumps each hair strand</li><li>Lightweight and colour safe formula</li><li>Sulphate, phosphate and paraben-free</li><li>Ideal for fine to medium hair<br/></li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $43.50.</p><p>MOROCCANOIL Extra Volume Conditioner increases volume while detangling, hydrating and protecting fine or limp hair. This body boosting conditioner infuses Argan Oil to deeply nourish fine strands, while a blend of Glycerin and Cocamide MEA moisturise and hydrate. This volumising conditioner softens the hair while increasing its natural shine, while added Tilia Tomentosa Bud Extract naturally plumps each hair strand to boost its fullness. With its lightweight and colour-safe formula, Extra Volume Conditioner increases lustre and reduces static for thicker feeling hair.<br/></p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Tilia Tomentosa Bud Extract</li><li>Glycerin</li><li>Rosemary Extract</li><li>Argan Oil</li><li>Cocamide MEA</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Water, Dimethicone, Cetearyl Alcohol, Fragrance, Behentrimonium Chloride , Canola Oil, Argania Spinosa (Argan) Kernel Oil, Nasturtium Officinale Leaf Extract , Allium Sativum (Garlic) Bulb Extract , Lamium Album Flower Extract , Pinus Sylvestris Bud Extract , Arctium Lappa Root Extract , Anthemis Nobilis Flower Extract , Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosmary) Leaf Extract , Hedera Helix (Ivy) Extract , Arnica Montana Flower Extract , Tilia To