(23, 'pure-blonde-booster-mask', 'Pure Blonde Booster Mask', 'A nourishing and clarifying hair mask designed to neutralise brassiness and cool warm tones. Smooth, hydrate and brighten blondes with Pure Blonde Booster Mask by Philip Kingsley.', '<ul><li>Nourishing and clarifying blonde booster mask</li><li>Instantly neutralises brassy tones to leave hair restored and clarified</li><li>Deeply conditions, smooths and hydrates</li><li>Increases hair strength and resistance to breakage </li><li>Draws moisture into the hair shaft to improve elasticity, moisture retention and flexibility </li><li>Violet micro-pigments correct yellow tones for that freshly coloured finish</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $34.00.</p>                Philip Kingsley Pure Blonde Booster Mask deeply nourishes and instantly neutralises brassy blondes, leaving hair feeling restored and looking clarified. This deeply conditioning formula features the perfect balance of violet micro-pigments, which correct yellow tones to reveal a freshly coloured look. Hydrolyzed Keratin targets the most damaged areas of the hair surface to replace lost keratin and maintain moisture. A blend of Magnesium Aspartate, Zinc Gluconate and Copper Gluconate cool warm tones, leaving hair bright and radiant. This purple toning mask draws in moisture to improve elasticity while leaving hair smooth, strong and hydrated.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Violet Pigments</li><li>Cationic Dye</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua/Water/Eau, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Behentrimonium Chloride, Cetrimonium Chloride, Hydrolyzed Vegetable Protein PG-Propyl Silanetriol, Hydrolyzed Oats, Laurdimonium Hydroxypropyl Hydrolyzed Keratin, Panthenol, Hydrolyzed Keratin, Amodimethicone, Trideceth-12, Ethylhexylglycerin, Isopropyl Alcohol, Disodium EDTA, Parfum (Fragrance), Benzyl Salicylate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Limonene, Phenoxyethanol, Potassium Sorbate, HC Blue No 2, CI 60730 (Ext. Violet 2).                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>After shampooing, gently work formula through the hair, avoiding the scalp. </li><li>Leave for 3 minutes if the hair is bleached, up to 5 minutes if dyed, and up to 10 minutes if naturally blonde. </li><li>Rinse thoroughly. </li><li>Use weekly. </li></ol>Timings should be halved for first use. Test a small section of the lightest hair before first use. Wait at least two weeks after colouring before using.                </div>', '82214_thumbnail_3.png', 5, 3, 4, '82214', 16, 33, 3.10404, 24, 0, '2022-02-02'),
