(Fragrance), Benzyl Salicylate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Limonene, Phenoxyethanol, Potassium Sorbate, HC Blue No 2, CI 60730 (Ext. Violet 2).                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>After shampooing, gently work through the hair, avoiding the scalp. </li><li> Leave for 3 minutes if the hair is bleached, up to 5 minutes if dyed, and up to 10 minutes if naturally blonde. </li><li> Rinse thoroughly. </li><li> Use weekly. </li></ol> Timings should be halved for first use. Test a small section of the lightest hair before first use. Wait at least two weeks after colouring before using.                </div>', '82218_thumbnail_3.png', 5, 3, 4, '82218', 32, 36, 1.28976, 4, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(25, 'intense-hair-treatment-kit', 'Intense Hair Treatment Kit', 'With the OLAPLEX Intensive Hair Treatment Kit, your clients can save $10 on the revolutionary bond building system.', '<p>OLAPLEX Intense Hair Treatment Kit includes:</p><ul><li>1 x <a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/hair-care/hair-treatments/colour-treatments/olaplex-no0-intense-bond-building-treatment-155ml-62120/\">No.0 Bond Building Treatment </a>to build bonds and prime hair for deeper repair</li><li>1 x <a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/hair-care/hair-treatments/colour-treatments/olaplex-no3-hair-perfector-treatment-100ml-62130/\">No.3 Hair Perfector </a>to continue the reparative effects of the OLAPLEX in-salon service</li><li>Consumer saves $10 RRP</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $89.95.</p><p>The OLAPLEX Intensive Hair Treatment Kit is the perfect take-home duo for your clients who regularly use the OLAPLEX system in salon. No.0 Intensive Bond Building Treatment starts by priming the hair for deeper repair, rebuilding bonds, strengthening and protecting the hair integrity. No.3 Hair Perfector continues the benefits of the OLAPLEX in-salon service by repairing any new damage and helping to increase the life and vibrancy of colour. When used as a two-part system, the Intensive Hair Treatment Kit is scientifically proven to result in 68% more repair while making the hair 3 times stronger. <br/></p>', '', '', '62013_thumbnail_0.png', 5, 2, 3, '62013', 39, 56, 2.42137, 43, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(26, 'silver-fx-lithium-cord/cordless-trimmer', 'Silver FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Trimmer', 'Great for clipper outlining and precise hair trimming, create defined hair styles with the BabylissPRO Silver FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Trimmer.', '<ul><li>BabylissPRO Hair Trimmer</li><li>For everyday precise shaping and definition</li><li>Corded and cordless design</li><li>DLC/Nickel Titanium coated blades</li><li>4 comb attachments</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $295.00.</p><p>A powerful and precise tool for your salon kit, the BabylissPRO Silver FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Trimmer features nickel titanium coated blades and a 6000 rpm Ferrari engine. Combining speed and precision, this is the ultimate hair trimming experience. <br/></p>', '', '', '78350_thumbnail_5.png', 6, 10, 4, '78350', 45, 59, 1.70732, 12, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(27, 'mini-blaze-cord/cordless-trimmer', 'Mini Blaze Cord/Cordless Trimmer', 'The Silver Bullet Mini Blaze Cord/Cordless Trimmer packs power, speed and breathtaking performance into a convenient size.', '<ul><li>Mini hair trimmer</li><li>Corded and cordless design </li><li>210 minutes cordless runtime</li><li>DLC non-irritating blade</li><li>Great for mobile barbers</li><li>3 comb attachments (1.5mm, 1mm, 0.5mm)</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $148.95.</p><p>Good things come in small packages. The Silver Bullet Mini Blaze Cord/Cordless Trimmer, packs power, speed and breathtaking performance into a convenient size. 210 minutes cordless run time, and two-hour charge courtesy of a lithium battery, this trimmer is always ready when you are.<br/></p>', '', '', '77395_thumbnail_5.png', 6, 11, 2, '77395', 39, 58, 3.58253, 8, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(28, 'white-fx-lithium-cord/cordless-clipper', 'White FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Clipper', 'The limited edition BabylissPRO White FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Clipper combines power with personality.', '<ul><li>White FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Clipper </li><li>High torque styler</li><li>Cord or cordless design</li><li>Hanging hook</li><li>8 comb attachments</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $395.00.</p><p>Part of a collaboration between three of the biggest names in barbering, the limited edition Influencer Collection BabylissPRO White FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Clipper features a titanium taper blade. Inspired by the sharp, intricate and cutting-edge designs of @robtheoriginal, its high torque, Ferrari engine combines power with cordless grooming, convenience. </p>', '', '', '78329_thumbnail_7.png', 6, 10, 2, '78329', 12, 30, 1.31663, 46, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(29, 'dynamic-duo-clipper-&-trimmer-set', 'Dynamic Duo Clipper & Trimmer Set', 'A one-stop grooming duo, the Silver Bullet Trimmer and Clipper Set is everything needed for all types of facial and hair grooming.', '<ul><li>Hair Trimmer and Clipper Set </li><li>1 x Professional Hair Clipper</li><li>1 x Trimmer </li><li>High performance grooming tools </li><li>Stainless Steel Blades </li><li>Extra length cords</li><li>Multiple comb attachments </li><li>Trimmer comes with scissors, comb, oil and pouch</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $136.00.</p><p>Some things are just better together, that\'s why the Silver Bullet Dynamic Duo Hair Trimmer and Clipper Set is such a great combo. With powerful mechanics and superior attachments, you\'re guaranteed smooth and stylish grooming results from these two high performance tools.<br/></p>', '', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\">                    Use as required, follow manufacturing instructions for setup and maintenance.                </div>', '77350_thumbnail_9.png', 6, 11, 4, '77350', 26, 41, 1.9574, 35, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(30, 'red-fx-lithium-cord/cordless-outliner-trimmer', 'Red FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Outliner Trimmer', 'Great for clipper outlining and precise hair trimming, experience 2 hours of cordless run time with BabylissPRO Red FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Outliner Trimmer.', '<ul><li>BabylissPRO Red FX Outliner Trimmer</li><li>For everyday precise shaping and definition</li><li>Corded and cordless design</li><li>2 hour runtime</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $320.00.</p><p>A powerful and precise tool for your salon kit, the BabylissPRO Red FX Lithium Cord/Cordless Outliner Trimmer features nickel titanium coated blades and a 6000 rpm Ferrari engine. Combining speed and precision, this is the ultimate hair trimming experience. <br/></p>', '', '', '78362_thumbnail_4.png', 6, 10, 1, '78362', 43, 58, 2.11908, 4, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(31, 'elasticizer-pre-shampoo-treatment', 'Elasticizer Pre-Shampoo Treatment', 'A multiple award winning pre-shampoo treatment designed to deliver elasticity, body and bounce to all hair textures. Reduce breakage and restore the hair\'s strength with Elasticizer by Philip Kingsley.', '<ul><li>Pre-shampoo treatment that delivers elasticity, body, bounce and shine to all hair textures</li><li>Hydrolyzed Elastin improves hair\'s tensile strength and stretch while reducing breakage and snapping</li><li>Castor Oil &amp; Glycerin seals in moisture for long-lasting hydration</li><li>Olive Oil, rich in Vitamin E, protects hair from UV damage while improving shine </li><li>Suitable for all hair types; all residue washes out, leaving hair in great condition without added weight </li><li>Paraben and fragrance free formulation</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $72.75.</p><p>Philip Kingsley\'s award-winning Elasticizer features a deeply conditioning formula to dramatically improve the hair\'s texture, strength and resistance to breakage. For clients who struggle to grow their hair past a certain length, regularly subject their hair to colour processing or heat styling, find other conditioning treatments too heavy, or just want healthy, beautiful hair all the time - Elasticizer is the perfect solution. Designed for use as a pre-shampoo treatment, this paraben free formulation uses Hydrolyzed Elastin to enhance elasticity, body and bounce while improving the hair\'s tensile strength. By restoring the hair\'s stretch, clients will experience less breakage and snapping. An infusion of Castor Oil and Glycerin helps the hair retain moisture so it doesn\'t dry out. Added Olive Oil, high in antioxidant Vitamin E and essential fatty acids, increases the hair\'s shine while protecting from UV damage. With regular, weekly usage, your clients can experience gradual improvements that last.</p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Hydrolyzed Elastin</li><li>Glycerin</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua (Water), Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Propylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Ethylhexyl Dimethyl PABA, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Cetrimonium Chloride, Amodimethicone, Phenoxyethanol, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Ethylhexylglycerin, Hydrolyzed Elastin, Trideceth-12, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid.                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply Elasticizer to wet hair before shampooing. </li><li>Dampen the hair and liberally apply to mid-lengths and ends. </li><li>Cover the hair with a shower cap or towel for 20 minutes. Elasticizer can be left for longer or overnight prior to rinsing. </li><li>Rinse thoroughly before shampooing and conditioning as normal. Elasticizer can be left in overnight. </li></ol>Do not use Elasticizer 72 hours before or after colour services as it might affect how the colour takes in this period only.                </div>', '82176_thumbnail_6.png', 7, 3, 2, '82176', 23, 30, 4.4015, 27, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(32, 'elasticizer-extreme-pre-shampoo-treatment', 'Elasticizer Extreme Pre-Shampoo Treatment', 'A pre-shampoo treatment designed to deliver elasticity, body and bounce to extremely damaged or African and Caribbean hair types. Reduce breakage and restore the hair\'s strength with Elasticizer Extreme by Philip Kingsley.', '<ul><li>Superb conditioning and moisturising pre-shampoo treatment </li><li>Reveals stronger, healthier hair with frequent use</li><li>Hydrolyzed Elastin adds strength, body and elasticity to retain moisture and reduce breakage</li><li>Castor Oil and Glycerin help to retain moisture</li><li>Olive Oil high in Vitamin E enhances shine </li><li>Designed for all variations of African and Caribbean hair</li><li>Also suitable for over processed and damaged Caucasian hair</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $77.00.</p>                Philip Kingsley Elasticizer Extreme is a superb conditioning and moisturising pre-shampoo treatment. It contains higher active doses of the ingredients found in Elasticizer.to address the unique structure, styling and grooming needs of African and Caribbean hair types. Hydrolyzed Elastin improves the hair\'s tensile strength while enhancing moisture retention, helping to reduce breakage and increase stretch. Castor Oil and Glycerin lock in moisture while Olive Oil high in Vitamin E and essential fatty acids boosts shine. Elasticizer Extreme can also be used on extremely dry and damaged Caucasian hair, or hair that has recently been bleached or had a colour strip service. With frequent use, Elasticizer Extreme reveals stronger, healthier hair with greater body, bounce and shine.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Castor Seed Oil</li><li>Hydrolyzed Elastin</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua/Water/Eau, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Propylene Glycol, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Ethylhexyl Dimethyl PABA, Amodimethicone, Polyquaternium-37, Diazolidinyl Urea, Silicone Quaternium-18, Propylene Glycol Dicaprylate/Dicaprate, Trideceth-12, Trideceth-6, Cetrimonium Chloride, Hydrolyzed Elastin, PPG-1 Trideceth-6, Phenoxyethanol, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Ethylhexylglycerin.                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply Elasticizer Extreme to wet hair before shampooing. </li><li>Dampen the hair and liberally apply to mid-lengths and ends.</li><li>Cover the hair with a shower cap or towel for 20 minutes. Elasticizer Extreme can be left for longer or overnight prior to rinsing. </li><li>Rinse thoroughly before shampooing and conditioning as normal. Elasticizer Extreme can be left in overnight. </li></ol>Do not use Elasticizer Extreme 72 hours before or after colour services as it might affect how the colour takes in this period only.                </div>', '82188_thumbnail_6.png', 7, 3, 1, '82188', 15, 18, 0.312153, 31, 100, '2022-02-02'),
