arkers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Hydrolyzed Elastin</li><li>Glycerin</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua (Water), Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Propylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Ethylhexyl Dimethyl PABA, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Cetrimonium Chloride, Amodimethicone, Phenoxyethanol, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Ethylhexylglycerin, Hydrolyzed Elastin, Trideceth-12, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid.                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply Elasticizer to wet hair before shampooing. </li><li>Dampen the hair and liberally apply to mid-lengths and ends. </li><li>Cover the hair with a shower cap or towel for 20 minutes. Elasticizer can be left for longer or overnight prior to rinsing. </li><li>Rinse thoroughly before shampooing and conditioning as normal. Elasticizer can be left in overnight. </li></ol>Do not use Elasticizer 72 hours before or after colour services as it might affect how the colour takes in this period only.                </div>', '82802_thumbnail_2.png', 7, 3, 1, '82802', 11, 20, 1.04894, 4, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(35, 'trichotherapy-tricho-pro-step-1', 'Trichotherapy Tricho Pro Step 1', 'A volumising protein spray to increase cuticle integrity and strength. Help to reduce hair loss caused by breakage with Tricho Pro Step 1 by Philip Kingsley.', '<ul><li>Volumising protein spray to help minimise hair loss caused by breakage</li><li>Quinoa Protein helps to repair damage, strengthen and protect the cuticle</li><li>Hydrolyzed Elastin increases moisture, shine and elasticity, making hair easier to comb</li><li>Polyamide-1 helps to volumise hair, create fullness and minimise frizz</li><li>6 week supply per 100ml bottle</li><li>Suitable for clients who experience hair shedding and want more volume</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $79.00.</p>                Philip Kingsley\'s revolutionary Trichotherapy range tackles common hair loss experienced in fine or thinning hair types. Tricho Pro Step 1 is a volumising protein spray formulated to help minimise hair fall caused by breakage. The use of Quinoa Protein, rich in all 8 amino acids, helps to repair this damage, strengthen and protect the cuticle. Hydrolyzed Elastin enhances the elasticity, moisture and shine of hair, making it easier to detangle to reduce breakage. Added Polyamide-1 creates more fullness and volume while minimising frizz. Each 100ml bottle offers a 6 week supply. Tricho Pro Step 1 is ideal for clients who experience additional hair shedding or a reduction in volume, and want to get the best from their hair. Clients can expect an improvement in hair quality, condition and strength after 3 months of use.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua (Water), Polysorbate 20, Glycerin, Citric Acid, Silicone Quaternium-16, Sodium Levulinate, PPG-12-PEG-50 Lanolin, Stearyl Dihydroxypropyldimonium Oligosaccharides, Isopropyl Myristate, Cetyl Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Sweet Almond Seedcake, Disodium EDTA, Parfum (Fragrance), Quaternium-91, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sodium Anisate, Undeceth-11, Dmdm Hydantoin, Panthenol, Propylene Glycol, Cyclopentasiloxane, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Cetrimonium Methosulfate, Butyloctanol, Polyimide-1, Chenopodium Quinoa Seed, C10-40 Isoalkylamidopropylethyldimonium Ethosulfate, Cyclohexasiloxane, Undeceth-5, Alcohol, Camellia Sinensis (Green TEA) Leaf Extract, Hydrolyzed Elastin, Phenoxyethanol, Tribehenin, Iodopropynyl Butylcarbamate, Sodium Benzoate, Ethylhexylglycerin.                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Spray Tricho Pro generously into mid-lengths and ends of clean, damp hair after shampooing and before combing. </li><li> Blow-dry in for a fuller, smoother finish or leave to air dry. </li><li>Use daily. </li></ol></div>', '82358_thumbnail_6.png', 7, 3, 3, '82358', 29, 47, 2.99783, 37, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(36, 'derma-activate-thickening-spray', 'Derma Activate Thickening Spray', 'A leave-in spray to thicken fine hair and prevent hair loss. Improve hair vitality, strength and elasticity with Derma Active Thickening Spray by Keune Care.', '<ul><li>Leave-in treatment spray decrease and prevent hair loss</li><li>Biotin strengthens the hair\'s natural Keratin structure</li><li>Panthenol regulates moisture while Proteins boost body and volume </li><li>Essential Mineral Complex nourishes and cares for the scalp</li><li>Vegan and cruelty-free</li><li>Recommended for delicate, fine, thinning and dull hair</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $31.50.</p>                With a diverse range of carefully crafted products to treat every hair concern, Keune Care offers hairdressers a trusted treatment program that tailors to any client. Formulated with a healthy scalp in mind, Keune Care features an Essential Mineral Complex to nourish and balance the hair\'s foundation, promoting sustainable hair quality. Zinc stimulates the development of new cells, while Copper encourages hair growth by boosting the formation of disulfide cross linkages. Silicon ensures the development of collagen and connective tissues, while Iron circulates oxygen to energise and invigorate the scalp for glossy hair growth. Magnesium sustains this energy production to ensure a continual, healthy mineral balance for a thriving scalp and deeply restored hair. Targeting delicate, thinning hair, Derma Active Thickening Lotion prevents excessive loss of hair by stimulating the scalp\'s metabolism; making hair more resistant to external influences. This leave-in treatment features Biotin, a form of Vitamin H, that boosts the hair\'s natural Keratin structure to decrease hair loss and improve elasticity. Panthenol regulates the moisture balance of the hair, while added proteins increase body and volume for improved strength and vitality. By using the full Derma Active range, hair and scalp are dramatically revitalised with stimulated hair growth and quality.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Panthenol</li><li>Zinc</li><li>Silicon</li><li>Magnesium</li><li>Iron</li><li>Copper</li><li>Wheat Protein</li><li>Biotin</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua (Water), Alcohol Denat., PVP, Propylene Glycol, Panthenol, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Sodium Benzoate, Parfum (Fragrance), Citric Acid, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Cocoyl Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Saccharomyces/Magnesium Ferment, Dipropylene Glycol, Saccharomyces/Iron Ferment, Sodium Chloride, Biotin, Saccharomyces/Zinc Ferment, Saccharomyces/Copper Ferment, Phenoxyethanol, Saccharomyces/Silicon Ferment, Benzyl Salicylate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Limonene, Linalool                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply section by section to damp hair. </li><li>Leave in. </li><li>Blow-dry and style as desired.</li></ol></div>', '31018_thumbnail_2.png', 8, 9, 4, '31018', 17, 31, 3.38676, 17, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(37, 'active-shock-concentrate-8x6ml', 'Active Shock Concentrate 8x6ml', 'An active concentrate for intensively preventing hair loss while increasing density and vitalising the scalp. Achieve beautiful, healthy hair with K.Therapy by Lakmé.', '<ul><li>Shock concentrate for intensive prevention of hair loss</li><li>Procapil improves blood circulation and hair density while preventing ageing </li><li>Olive Leaf Extract regulates and normalises the activity of the sebaceous gland</li><li>Bioactive Peptides vitalise scalp cells and hair follicles</li><li>Dermatologically tested</li><li>Recommended for weak and devitalised hair</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $103.50.</p>                K.Therapy by Lakmé provides comfort and well-being with dermatologically tested products that aid in the treatment of hair and scalp problems. K.Therapy Active Concentrate intensively prevents hair loss while increasing the density of hair. Procapil stimulates cell dynamism to delay hair loss, actively preventing ageing while improving blood circulation. Olive Leaf Extract regulates and normalises the activity of the sebaceous gland, reducing production of DHT. Added Bioactive Peptides further regulate the correct development of the hair cycle, vitalising scalp cells and hair follicles. This hair loss treatment infuses water from the Zermatt Glacier consisting of minerals and trace elements with decongestant properties soften and protect the skin. Achieve increased vitality and density while actively preventing hair loss.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Bioactive Peptides</li><li>Olive Leaf Extract</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Alcohol Denat., Butylene Glycol, Peg-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Panthenol, Fragrance (Parfum), Milk Protein (Lactis Proteinum), Ppg-26-Buteth-26, Acetyl Cysteine, Acetyl Methionine, Panthenyl Ethyl Ether, Lactic Acid, Citric Acid, Inositol, Lactose, Sodium Citrate, Apigenin, Lecithin, Oleanolic Acid, Biotinoyl Tripeptide-1                    </div></div>', '', '59356_thumbnail_2.png', 8, 12, 1, '59356', 21, 34, 2.29736, 3, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(38, 'active-fortifying-mask', 'Active Fortifying Mask', 'A fortifying mask for boosting strength and shine while repairing weak, devitalised hair. Achieve beautiful, healthy hair with K.Therapy by Lakmé.', '<ul><li>Fortifying mask for stronger, more hair</li><li>Ceramide Strength Complex reinforces and repairs the hair fibre</li><li>Filmogenic Silicones make hair smoother, shinier and easier to comb</li><li>Provides energy and vigour while preventing ageing of hair</li><li>Fragrance notes of Water, Geranium &amp; Citrus Blossom</li><li>Dermatologically tested</li><li>Recommended for weak and devitalised hair<br/></li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $49.95.</p>                K.Therapy by Lakmé provides comfort and well-being with dermatologically tested products that aid in the treatment of hair and scalp problems. K.Therapy Active Fortifying Mask provides strength, resistance and shine for weak and devitalised hair. This hair loss treatment uses a Ceramide Strength Complex to reinforce and repair the hair fibre while penetrating its interior, leaving hair stronger and healthier with fuller body. Filmogenic Silicones repair damaged ends, making hair smoother, shinier and easier to comb. Water from the Zermatt Glacier consisting of minerals and trace elements with decongestant properties soften and protect the skin. Fragrance notes of Water, Geranium and Citrus Blossom create a truly soothing experience. Achieve greater energy and vigour while preventing the ageing of hair.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Ceramide</li><li>Filmogenic Silicones</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Cyclopentasiloxane, Dimethiconol, Fragrance (Parfum), Cetearyl Alcohol, Polyquaternium-37, Dipalmitoylethyl Hydroxyethylmonium Methosulfate, Propylene Glycol Dicaprylate/Dicaprate, Dimethicone Peg-8 Meadowfoamate, Cetear