(39, 'derma-activate-lotion', 'Derma Activate Lotion', 'An intensive treatment to reduce temporary hair loss and thinning. Improve hair vitality, strength and elasticity with Derma Active Lotion by Keune Care.', '<ul><li>Intense leave-in treatment to prevent temporary hair loss and thinning </li><li>Biotin strengthens the hair\'s natural Keratin structure</li><li>Liposomes transport growth promoting ingredients to the scalp</li><li>Caffeine stimulates blood circulation while Takanal activates cell metabolism </li><li>Essential Mineral Complex nourishes and cares for the scalp</li><li>Cruelty free</li><li>Recommended for delicate, fine, thinning and dull hair<br/></li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $31.50.</p>                With a diverse range of carefully crafted products to treat every hair concern, Keune Care offers hairdressers a trusted treatment program that tailors to any client. Formulated with a healthy scalp in mind, Keune Care features an Essential Mineral Complex to nourish and balance the hair\'s foundation, promoting sustainable hair quality. Zinc stimulates the development of new cells, while Copper encourages hair growth by boosting the formation of disulfide cross linkages. Silicon ensures the development of collagen and connective tissues, while Iron circulates oxygen to energise and invigorate the scalp for glossy hair growth. Magnesium sustains this energy production to ensure a continual, healthy mineral balance for a thriving scalp and deeply restored hair. Targeting delicate, fine and thinning hair, Derma Active Lotion prevents excessive loss of hair by stimulating the scalp\'s metabolism; making hair more resistant to external influences. This leave-in treatment features Biotin, a form of Vitamin H, that boosts the hair\'s natural Keratin structure to decrease hair loss and improve elasticity. Takanal activates cell metabolism to stimulate hair growth, while Caffeine invigorates blood circulation to create a longer hair growth phase. Added Liposomes transport these active ingredients directly to the scalp for more effective prevention of incidental hair loss. By using the full Derma Active range, hair and scalp are dramatically revitalised with increased hair quality, shine and health.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Biotin</li><li>Ginseng</li><li>Zinc</li><li>Silicon</li><li>Magnesium</li><li>Iron</li><li>Copper</li><li>Caffeine</li><li>Lipsomes</li><li>Takanal</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua (Water), Alcohol Denat., Butylene Glycol, Glycerin, Lecithin, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Sodium Benzoate, Caffeine, Parfum (Fragrance), 3-Aminopropane Sulfonic Acid, Sodium Chondroitin Sulfate, Propylene Glycol, Citric Acid, Saccharomyces/Magnesium Ferment, Dipropylene Glycol, Panax Ginseng Root Extract, Saccharomyces/Iron Ferment, Biotin, Quaternium-51, Saccharomyces/Zinc Ferment, Quartz, Saccharomyces/Copper Ferment, Saccharomyces/Silicon Ferment, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid, Benzyl Salicylate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Limonene, Linalool                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Shampoo with Derma Active Shampoo then towel-dry. </li><li>Apply Derma Active Lotion to the scalp and massage using fingers with circular movements. </li><li>Do not rinse. </li><li>Style as desired. </li></ol><ul><li> For preventive use: 1 - 2 times a week. </li><li>For intensive use: 3 - 4 times a week over 11 weeks. </li><li>For maintenance: 2 - 3 times a week.</li></ul></div>', '31016_thumbnail_3.png', 8, 9, 1, '31016', 28, 47, 0.117666, 5, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(40, 'active-lotion', 'Active Lotion', 'A fortifying lotion that prevents hair loss and strengthens the hair fibre while restoring vitality to the scalp. Achieve beautiful, healthy hair with K.Therapy by Lakmé.', '<ul><li>Fortifying lotion for restoring vitality to the hair and scalp</li><li>Procapil prevents hair loss and strengthens the hair fibre</li><li>Olive Leaf Extract regulates and normalises the activity of the sebaceous gland</li><li>Bioactive Peptides vitalise scalp cells and hair follicles while correcting vitamin deficiencies</li><li>Fragrance notes of Water, Geranium &amp; Citrus Blossom</li><li>Dermatologically tested</li><li>Recommended for weak and devitalised hair</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $46.50.</p>                K.Therapy by Lakmé provides comfort and well-being with dermatologically tested products that aid in the treatment of hair and scalp problems. K.Therapy Active Lotion acts at several levels to fortify the hair and restore vitality. Procapil stimulates cell dynamism to delay hair loss, actively preventing ageing while improving blood circulation. Olive Leaf Extract regulates and normalises the activity of the sebaceous gland, reducing production of DHT, while an infusion of vitamins simulate cell metabolism and correct deficiencies. Added Bioactive Peptides further regulate the correct development of the hair cycle, vitalising scalp cells and hair follicles. This hair loss treatment infuses water from the Zermatt Glacier consisting of minerals and trace elements with decongestant properties soften and protect the skin. Fragrance notes of Water, Geranium and Citrus Blossom soothe the senses. Restore vitality to the hair and scalp while actively preventing hair loss.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Bioactive Peptides</li><li>Olive Leaf Extract</li><li>Vitamin A</li><li>Vitamin E</li><li>Procapil</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Alcohol Denat., Butylene Glycol, Peg-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Panthenol, Fragrance (Parfum), Menthol, Peg-35 Castor Oil, Horse Chestnut (Aesculus Hippocastanum) Extract, Milk Protein (Lactis Proteinum), Tocopherol, Ppg-26-Buteth-26, Acetyl Cysteine, Acetyl Methionine, Inositol, Panthenyl Ethyl Ether, Calcium Pantothenate, Citric Acid, Lactose, Linoleic Acid, Polysorbate 20, Retynil Palmitate, Sodium Citrate, Lecithin, Apigenin, Biotin, Oleanolic Acid, Biotinoyl Tripeptide-1                    </div></div>', '', '59360_thumbnail_3.png', 8, 12, 4, '59360', 22, 40, 3.35744, 0, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(41, 'ultimate-blonde-pack', 'Ultimate Blonde Pack', 'The MOROCCANOIL Ultimate Blonde Pack features the Blonde Perfecting Purple Shampoo & Conditioner duo plus the light treatment - perfect for maintaining healthy blonde hair.', '<div>MOROCCANOIL Ultimate Blonde Pack includes:</div><ul><li>1 x <a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/hair-care/shampoo/hair-colour-shampoo/moroccanoil-blonde-perfecting-purple-shampoo-70ml-41700/\">Blonde Perfecting Purple Shampoo 70ml</a></li><li>1 x <a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/hair-care/conditioner/colour-conditioner/moroccanoil-blonde-perfecting-purple-conditioner-70ml-41703/\">Blonde Perfecting Purple Conditioner 70ml</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/hair-care/hair-treatments/hydration-hair-treatments/moroccanoil-light-treatment-25ml-42028/\">1 x Light Treatment 25ml</a></li><li>Eradicate brassiness with Blonde Perfecting Shampoo and Conditioner</li><li>Style, condition and exude radiant shine with Light Treatment</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $34.95.</p>', '', '', '41714_thumbnail_3.png', 9, 1, 3, '41714', 33, 44, 2.89732, 15, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(42, 'swimcap-water-resistant-mask', 'Swimcap Water Resistant Mask', 'A water resistant hair mask perfect for blondes and swimmers. Shield hair from chlorine and salt water while providing UV protection. with Swimcap by Philip Kingsley', '<ul><li>Protective cream designed to shield hair from chlorine and salt water</li><li>Water resistant formula provides protection until washed out with shampoo</li><li>Hydrolyzed Elastin adds strength, body and elasticity while reducing breakage</li><li>Natural oils hydrate hair and lock-in moisture</li><li>Deeply nourishing - leaves hair looking and feeling like silk</li><li>Prevents blonde hair from turning green in chlorinated water</li><li>Ideal for clients who regularly swim and want to prevent discolouration and dehydration</li><li>Perfect for clients who want to protect their hair on holiday</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $42.90.</p>                Philip Kingsley Swimcap Water Resistant Mask was originally developed for the US Olympic Synchronized Swimming Team. Today it is a must-have in summer and for swimmers year-round. This water-resistant conditioning treatment protects against the drying and damaging effects of both chlorinated and salt water, extending the life of colour-treated hair and preventing blondes from turning green. The use of Hydrolyzed Elastin adds strength, body and elasticity to prevent breakage. A blend of Castor Oil and Olive Oil help lock-in moisture while improving shine. Swimcap is UV resistant, helping to protect hair from the sun. This leave-in treatment is perfect for clients who regularly swim and want to guard their hair against discolouration and dehydration. It\'s also great for those going on holiday to keep their hair healthy and protected while away.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Castor Seed Oil</li><li>Hydrolyzed Elastin</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua/Water/Eau, Ricinus Communis Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Propylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Dimethicone, Ethylhexyl Dimethyl PABA, Glycerin, Cetrimonium Chloride, Hydrolyzed Elastin, Phenoxyethanol, DMDM Hydantoin, Ethylhexylglycerin, Parfum (Fragrance), Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Hexyl Cinnamal, Citronellol, Linalool, Butylphenyl Methylpropional, Limonene, Benzyl Salicylate, Geraniol.                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply in sections to damp hair. </li><li>Leave the treatment on the hair to guard against effects of sun and water, while sunbathing and swimming. Create a slicked back look by applying Swimcap and pulling the hair into a bun or ponytail. </li><li>To remove, rinse well then double shampoo using the appropriate Philip Kingsley Shampoo. </li><li>Follow with Conditioner and Scalp Toner.</li></ol></div>', '82170_thumbnail_2.png', 9, 3, 4, '82170', 40, 60, 2.09275, 13, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(43, 'the-great-hydrator-moisture-mask', 'The Great Hydrator Moisture Mask', 'An intense hydrating treatment for dry, colour-treated hair. Restore moisture, softness and radiant shine with The Great Hydrator Moisture Mask by Evo.', '<ul><li>Restorative mask to improve softness, detangling and manageability</li><li>Seals the cuticle to lock-in moisture and minimise frizz</li><li>Argan Oil and Glycerin deeply moisturise </li><li>Amodimethicone boosts combability and shine</li><li>Oriental, woody, floral and musky fragrance notes</li><li>Vegan and cruelty free</li><li>Made without sulphates, parabens or gluten</li><li>Recommended for dry, colour-treated hair</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $38.00.</p><p>Evo The Great Hydrator Moisture Mask is an intense, natural treatment vegan formula designed to improve dry, colour-treated hair. An infusion of Argan Oil and Glycerin seals the hair cuticle while locking in essential moisture; reducing breakage and minimising frizz by controlling the impacts of humidity. Added Amodimethicone improves the manageability of hair, making it easier to detangle while imparting natural shine. This moisture mask features oriental, woody, floral and musky fragrance notes. Pair The Great Hydrator weekly with The Therapist Hydrating Shampoo and Conditioner for softer, silkier hair.<br/></p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Amodimethicone</li><li>Argan Oil</li><li>Glycerin</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Isopropyl Myristate, Behentrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Stearate, Glycerin, Isopropyl Alcohol, Acetamide Mea, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Amodimethicone, Parfum, Phenoxyethanol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Hydrolyzed Quinoa, Benzoic Acid, Trideceth – 15, Trideceth -3, Citric Acid, Dehydroacetic Acid, Butylene Glycol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Alcohol, Acetic Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Coumarin, Benzyl Salicylate.                    </div></div>', '', '39267_thumbnail_5.png', 9, 4, 4, '39267', 23, 42, 3.24629, 6, 100, '2022-02-02');
