(44, 'no.8-bond-intense-moisture-mask', 'No.8 Bond Intense Moisture Mask', 'A highly concentrated 4-in-1 reparative hair mask to moisturise, add shine, build body & repair damaged hair. Improve hair texture & strength with OLAPLEX No.8 Bond Intense Moisture Mask.', '<ul><li>Highly concentrated 4-in-1 reparative mask</li><li>Features patented OLAPLEX Bond Building technology</li><li>Enhances shine and body</li><li>Infuses moisture into damaged, dry hair</li><li>Dramatically smooths and softens </li><li>Features an airless pump for measured dosing</li><li>Vegan, cruelty free and colour safe</li><li>Made without sulphates, phthalates, parabens or gluten</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $49.95.</p>                Infused with patented OLAPLEX Bond Building technology, the highly anticipated No.8 Bond Intense Moisture Mask creates a 4-in-1 treatment effect on dry, damaged hair. This reparative mask helps <a href=\"/the-hub/news/new-olaplex-no.8-bond-intense-moisture-mask/\">strengthen, hydrate and moisturise hair</a>, leaving it with more body, more shine and dramatically smoother. This formula is highly concentrated - so you\'ll only need a small amount for big results, and an airless pump mechanism makes it easy to measure dosing. No.8 Bond Intense Moisture Mask is the perfect treatment for clients post colour, and a great take-home option to keep hair healthy and strong between salon visits. OLAPLEX is 100% vegan and colour safe, and is made without sulphates, phthalates, parabens or gluten.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Water(Aqua/Eau), Dimethicone, Cetyl Alcohol, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Glycerin, Stearyl Alcohol, Ethylhexyl Olivate, Behentrimonium Chloride, Cetrimonium Bromide, Limnanthes Alba (Meadowfoam) Seed Oil, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Oil, Quaternium-80, Squalane, Rosa Canina (Rose Hip) Seed Extract, Ceramide AP, Ceramide NP, Hydrolyzed Jojoba Esters, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium PCA, Bis-Aminopropyl Diglycol Dimaleate, Arginine, Jojoba Esters, Panthenol, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Seed Oil, Cannabis Sativa (Hemp) Seed Oil, Glycine, Alanine, Serine, Valine, Isoleucine, Proline, Threonine, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Histidine, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Phenylalanine, Aspartic Acid, PCA, Phosphatidylcholine, Citric Acid, Sodium Lactate, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Phenoxyethanol, Bis-Cetearyl Amodimethicone, Propylene Glycol, Isopropyl Alcohol, Sodium Nitrate, Tocopherol, Fragrance (Parfum), Citral, Hexyl Cinnamal, Limonene                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply to clean, damp hair from mid-lengths to ends. Use sparingly on roots.</li><li>Start with 2 pumps for shoulder length hair. Use more for longer or thicker hair, and less for fine or short hair.</li><li>Work through hair with fingers, then leave for 10 minutes.</li><li>Rinse fully and style as usual. </li></ol><ul><li>Use weekly for best results.</li><li>For the deepest repair, use in conjunction with No.0 Intense Bond Building Treatment and No.3 Hair Perfector.</li></ul></div>', '62195_thumbnail_7.jpg', 9, 2, 3, '62195', 11, 27, 1.20214, 46, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(45, 'the-great-hydrator-moisture-mask', 'The Great Hydrator Moisture Mask', 'An intense hydrating treatment for dry, colour-treated hair. Restore moisture, softness and radiant shine with The Great Hydrator Moisture Mask by Evo.', '<ul><li>Restorative mask to improve softness, detangling and manageability</li><li>Seals the cuticle to lock-in moisture and minimise frizz</li><li>Argan Oil and Glycerin deeply moisturise </li><li>Amodimethicone boosts combability and shine</li><li>Oriental, woody, floral and musky fragrance notes</li><li>Vegan and cruelty free</li><li>Made without sulphates, parabens or gluten</li><li>Recommended for dry, colour-treated hair</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $7.00.</p><p>Evo The Great Hydrator Moisture Mask is an intense, natural treatment vegan formula designed to improve dry, colour-treated hair. An infusion of Argan Oil and Glycerin seals the hair cuticle while locking in essential moisture; reducing breakage and minimising frizz by controlling the impacts of humidity. Added Amodimethicone improves the manageability of hair, making it easier to detangle while imparting natural shine. This moisture mask features oriental, woody, floral and musky fragrance notes. Pair The Great Hydrator weekly with The Therapist Hydrating Shampoo and Conditioner for softer, silkier hair.<br/></p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Amodimethicone</li><li>Argan Oil</li><li>Glycerin</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Isopropyl Myristate, Behentrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Stearate, Glycerin, Isopropyl Alcohol, Acetamide Mea, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Amodimethicone, Parfum, Phenoxyethanol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Hydrolyzed Quinoa, Benzoic Acid, Trideceth – 15, Trideceth -3, Citric Acid, Dehydroacetic Acid, Butylene Glycol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Alcohol, Acetic Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Coumarin, Benzyl Salicylate.                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply to wet hair. </li><li>Leave for 5 minutes and rinse. </li><li>Use at least weekly depending on hair condition. </li></ol>Tip: For softer, more manageable hair, use The Great Hydrator weekly after shampooing and follow with conditioner.                </div>', '39509_thumbnail_2.png', 9, 4, 4, '39509', 31, 47, 0.348505, 23, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(46, 'flaky-itchy-scalp-shampoo', 'Flaky Itchy Scalp Shampoo', 'This award winning shampoo has been specially formulated to relieve scalp irritation and clear hair of flakes and build up. Soothe and calm the scalp with Flaky Itchy Scalp Shampoo by Philip Kingsley.', '<ul><li>Award winning formula designed to relieve irritated scalps and clear hair of flakes and build up</li><li>Gentle and soothing, making it suitable for daily use</li><li>Piroctone Olamine protects the skin against bacteria and relieves itching caused by dandruff </li><li>Lauryl Betaine mildly cleanses the scalp without causing redness</li><li>Features a delicate, apple fragrance</li><li>Ideal for flaky, itchy scalps</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $3.95.</p>                Philip KIngsley\'s award winning Flaky Itchy Scalp Shampoo was specially formulated to relieve irritated scalps and help clear the hair of flakiness and build up. This scalp shampoo is based on the Philip Kingsley Trichological Clinic formulation originally created for Sir Laurence Olivier. Unlike other anti-dandruff shampoos, Flaky Itchy will not dry the scalp out or strip the hair of any colour, making it extremely gentle and soothing. Mild enough for daily use, this shampoo uses Lauryl Betaine as a cleansing agent to remove dirt and oil without causing redness or irritation. Piroctone Olamine helps protect against bacteria and reduce flaking and itching commonly caused by dandruff. Flaky Itchy Scalp Shampoo is ideal for clients who suffer from dandruff or Seborrheic Dermatitis. It\'s also suitable for those with itchy or oily scalp, and men or teens who want to control hormone related scalp issues.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Lauryl Betaine</li><li>Octopirox</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua/Water/Eau, TEA-Lauryl Sulfate, Lauryl Betaine, PEG-4 Rapeseedamide, Piroctone Olamine, Citric Acid, Parfum (Fragrance), Sodium Chloride                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply Flaky/Itchy Scalp Shampoo to wet hair. </li><li>Lather with a gentle kneading of the scalp for 60 seconds. </li><li>Rinse and repeat, if necessary. </li><li>Use daily until the scalp is clear, and thereafter at regular intervals, as required.</li><li>Use in combination with Flaky/Itchy Scalp Toner and Exfoliating Scalp Mask for a 3-step regime for combating dandruff and irritation. </li><li>Use as a clarifying shampoo if clients frequently use styling products, or don\'t wash their hair regularly. </li><li>Flaky/Itchy Shampoo can be diluted with water for use on babies with cradle cap.</li></ol></div>', '82800_thumbnail_1.png', 10, 3, 1, '82800', 29, 40, 3.06263, 19, 100, '2022-02-02'),
