(48, 'flaky-itchy-scalp-dry-shampoo', 'Flaky Itchy Scalp Dry Shampoo', 'A dry shampoo that instantly cools and soothes itchy scalp. Eliminate dandruff and refresh the scalp with Flaky/Itchy Scalp Dry Shampoo by Philip Kingsley.', '<ul><li>Dry shampoo specially designed to target dandruff and scalp irritations</li><li>Aloe Vera helps relieve itchiness and irritation</li><li>Bisabolol soothes and calms he skin</li><li>Zinc PCA with anti-bacterial and anti-fungal properties reduces build-up on the scalp</li><li>Refreshes the scalp between washes and absorbs excess oil</li><li>Suitable for any hair texture</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $56.00.</p>                The first of its kind, Philip Kingsley Flaky/Itchy Scalp Dry Shampoo is specially designed to target the root cause of dandruff and alleviate scalp irritations. This dry shampoo uses Aloe Vera to relieve itchiness and irritation, while Bisabolol (a derivative of Chamomile) instantly cools and soothes. The use of Zinc PCA helps to reduce bacterial and fungal properties that can cause build-ups on the scalp. Flaky/Itchy Scalp Dry Shampoo is ideal for clients who experience itchiness between shampoos and want to refresh their hair and scalp. It\'s great for instant relief on-the-g, and leaves hair looking fresh and clean.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Lauryl Betaine</li><li>Octopirox</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Butane, Isobutane, Propane, Alcohol denat., Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Aluminum Starch Octenylsuccinate, Parfum (Fragrance), Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice, Dicocoylethyl Hydroxyethylmonium Methosulfate, Aqua/Water/Eau, Glycerin, Climbazole, Menthyl Lactate, Propylene Glycol, Bisabolol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Potassium Sorbate                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Shake well before use.</li><li>Keep nozzle 30cm away from hair and spray onto roots.</li><li>Leave for 10 seconds, then massage into hair and scalp.</li><li>Style as desired.</li></ol></div>', '82312_thumbnail_3.png', 10, 3, 4, '82312', 39, 47, 4.55933, 24, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(49, 'no-scent-no-colour-shampoo', 'No Scent No Colour Shampoo', 'A fragrance free shampoo for extra gentle hair cleansing. Leave hair shiny, soft and manageable with No Scent No Colour Shampoo by Philip Kingsley.', '<ul><li>Fragrance, colour, paraben and SLS free formula</li><li>Designed for extra gentle hair cleansing - suitable for daily use</li><li>Created to be mild enough for those undergoing chemo/radiation therapy</li><li>Lauryl Betaine gently cleanses the scalp without causing redness or irritation</li><li>Glycerides deliver moisture and manageability, leaving hair soft and supple</li><li>Designed for sensitive scalps and hair</li></ul>                Philip Kingsley No Scent No Colour Shampoo is specially formulated without fragrances, colours, parabens and SLS - making it ideal for sensitive scalps and hair. This gentle shampoo features Lauryl Betaine, a mild but effective cleansing agent that clears the scalp without causing redness or irritation. The use of Glycerides deliver moisture and manageability to the hair, ensuring it\'s left soft and supple. No Scent No Colour has been crafted for clients who are sensitive to cosmetic products, or dislike colour and fragrance in their hair products. It\'s a great choice for those undergoing or recovering from chemo/radiation therapy, or those who are trying to maintain the effects of a keratin treatment.', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Glycerin</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua/Water/Eau, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Lauroyl Sarcosinate, Caprylyl/Capryl Glucoside, PEG-90 Glyceryl Isosterate, Sodium Chloride, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Citric Acid, Silicone Quaternium-18, Laureth-2, Trideceth-6, Disodium EDTA, Polyquaternium-7, Trideceth-12, Isopropyl Alcohol, Sodium Cocoyl Hydrolyzed Amaranth Protein, Glycerin, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract, Ethylhexylglycerin, Phenoxyethanol, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate.                    </div></div>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Apply No Scent No Colour Shampoo to wet hair. </li><li>Lather with a gentle kneading of the scalp. </li><li>Rinse and repeat if necessary. </li><li>Follow with No Scent No Colour Conditioner and Scalp Toner. </li><li>Use on clients whose scalp has become sensitive during colouring or chemical services.</li></ol></div>', '82468_thumbnail_2.png', 10, 3, 4, '82468', 13, 20, 4.07143, 14, 100, '2022-02-02'),
