(51, 'perfect-cleanse-shampoo-with-pump', 'Perfect Cleanse Shampoo with Pump', 'A micellar shampoo that cleanses while detoxifying for soft, shiny, protected hair. Gently give the hair and scalp a deep wash while capturing residue and impurities with TEKNIA Perfect Cleanse by Lakmé.', '<p>This kit includes:</p><ul><li>1 x <a href=\"/hair-care/shampoo/cleansing-clarifying-shampoo/teknia-organic-perfect-cleanse-shampoo-1l-56376/\">Perfect Cleanse Shampoo</a></li><li>1 x <a href=\"/salon-supplies/sundries/pumps/teknia-organic-teknia-pump-for-bottles-1l-56609/\">TEKNIA Pump for Bottles</a></li></ul><ul><li>Micellar shampoo that deeply and gently cleanses</li><li>Micellae capture residue and impurities, keeping the structure of the hair intact</li><li>Fusion of Mediterranean Fruits naturally protects, moisturises and softens hair and scalp</li><li>Anti-bacterial and detoxifying</li><li>Refreshing fragrance of Fennel Essential Oil</li><li>Vegan formula free of parabens, mineral oils and colourants</li><li>Suitable for all hair types</li><li>Comes with bonus pump</li></ul><p>TEKNIA Perfect Cleanse Shampoo by Lakmé intensely cleanses the hair and scalp, protecting it from impurities, grease and minerals found in hard water. This vegan formula uses micelles to achieve a deep and delicate clean that is soft on the hair fibre; leaving its structure untouched. An infusion of Mediterranean Fruit Acids (lemon, grape and apple) work to detoxify and protect the hair from hard water while boosting its natural hydration. The combination of these fruits provide anti-limescale benefits while they moisturise. Perfect Cleanse Shampoo is free of parabens, mineral oils and colourants, while its antibacterial properties protect the hair and scalp. Achieve softer, shinier hair with this powerful, deep cleansing solution.<br/></p>', '', '', '56376_thumbnail_2.png', 11, 7, 2, '56376', 35, 52, 0.191436, 15, 100, '2022-02-02'),
