(55, 'normal-persons-daily-shampoo', 'Normal Persons Daily Shampoo', 'A deep cleansing, sulphate and paraben-free shampoo to remove product build-up. Balance and invigorate the scalp with Normal Persons Shampoo by Evo.', '<ul><li>Sulphate-free, emulsifying cleansers deeply clean and reduce excess oil</li><li>Peppermint Oil cools and stimulates the scalp</li><li>Panthenol locks in moisture while boosting natural shine</li><li>Aromatic, minty, tea, geranium and green fragrance notes</li><li>Vegan and cruelty free</li><li>Made without sulphates, parabens or gluten</li><li>Suitable for all hair types; especially oily hair</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $38.00.</p><p>Evo Normal Persons Daily Shampoo features a mild, sulphate-free formula that stimulates and invigorates the scalp. Emulsifying cleansers deeply clean while eradicating impurities and product build-up. An infusion of Peppermint Oil balances, stimulates and cools the scalp, reducing excess oil. Added Panthenol locks in the hair\'s moisture while boosting natural shine. This clarifying shampoo strengthens hair by reducing breakage; seamlessly improving combability and manageability. Daily Shampoo features minty, tea, geranium and green fragrance notes. Use Daily Shampoo in conjunction with Normal Persons Daily Conditioner for the deepest clean.<br/></p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Panthenol</li><li>Peppermint Oil</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua, Sodium Lauroyl Methyl Isethionate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Peg-150 Disterate, Peg-12 Dimethicone, Parfum, Phenoxyethanol, Hydrolyzed Quinoa, Methyl Lactate, Peg-6 Isolauryl Thioether, Tetrasodium Edta, Panthenol, Benzoic Acid, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Oil, Dehydroacetic Acid, Butylene Glycol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Linalool, Limonene, Citronellol, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol                    </div></div>', '', '39223_thumbnail_5.png', 11, 4, 4, '39223', 16, 18, 3.93554, 32, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(56, 'normal-persons-daily-conditioner', 'Normal Persons Daily Conditioner', 'A light-weight conditioner to minimise excess oil. Balance and invigorate the scalp with Normal Persons Conditioner by Evo.', '<ul><li>Anti-static conditioning agents minimise frizz and promote softness</li><li>Hydrolyzed Quinoa strengthens and protects while retaining colour vibrancy</li><li>Peppermint Oil cools and stimulates the scalp, reducing excess oil</li><li>Aromatic, minty, tea, geranium and green fragrance notes</li><li>Vegan and cruelty free</li><li>Made without sulphates, parabens or gluten</li><li>Suitable for all hair types; especially oily hair</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $38.00.</p><p>Evo Normal Persons Daily Conditioner features a light-weight, anti-static formula to naturally minimise frizz while nourishing and softening hair. An infusion of Peppermint Oil balances, stimulates and cools the scalp, reducing excess oil. Added Hydrolyzed Quinoa strengthens and protects the hair fibre, helping to retain colour vibrancy. This stimulating conditioner strengthens hair by reducing breakage; seamlessly improving combability and manageability. Daily Conditioner features minty, tea, geranium and green fragrance notes. Use Daily Conditioner in conjunction with Normal Persons Daily Shampoo for a balancing effect.<br/></p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Emulsifying Agent</li><li>Peppermint Oil</li><li>Quinoa</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua, Cetyl Alcohol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Isopropyl Myristate, Parfum, Phenoxyethanol, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Oil, Methyl Lactate, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Cetrimonium Chloride, Quaternium-80, Tocopheryl Acetate, Panthenol, Peg-8 Isolauryl Thioether, Cetyl Pca, Butylene Glycol, Hydrolyzed Quinoa, Dehydroacetic Acid, Ethylhexylglycerin, Benzoic Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Linalool,Limonene, Citronellol, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol                    </div></div>', '', '39231_thumbnail_5.png', 12, 4, 1, '39231', 41, 54, 2.37, 42, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(57, 'daily-conditioner', 'Daily Conditioner', 'A lightweight, moisturising conditioner formulated for daily use. Keep the scalp cool and the hair soft with Reuzel Daily Conditioner.', '<ul><li>Thoroughly conditions hair, leaving the scalp cool and refreshed</li><li>T4 Tonic Blend strengthens and adds shine to hair while tightening pores</li><li>Coconut and sustainable Palm Oil thicken and protect the hair</li><li>Formulated for effective degreasing</li><li>Suitable for use on all hair types</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $36.00.</p>                Reuzel Daily Conditioner leaves the hair and scalp feeling cool and refreshed, with a light detangling action perfect for everyday use. Daily Conditioner features Reuzel\'s unique T4 Tonic Blend of Witch Hazel, Nettle Leaf, Rosemary and Horsetail Root to strengthen, moisturise and add shine to hair while naturally tightening pores. This formula features Coconut Oil and sustainable Palm oil to thicken and protect the hair. Daily Conditioner works seamlessly with Daily Shampoo and Scrub Shampoo for a total degreasing effect.', '', '', '06311_thumbnail_1.png', 12, 13, 4, '06311', 33, 41, 0.457174, 36, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(58, 'daily-conditioner', 'Daily Conditioner', 'A daily hydrating conditioner suitable for all hair types to leave the hair soft and easy to detangle.', '<ul><li>Lightweight and gentle enough for daily use</li><li>Nourishing ingredients to promote healthy and shiny hair</li><li>Free from gluten, parabens and mineral oils</li><li>Vegan friendly</li><li>Suitable for all hair types</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $16.95.</p><p>Suitable for all hair types, 360 Daily Conditioner helps to fortify and revitalise hair with its regenerating formulation enriched with Calendula and Chamomile. Leaving hair soft and easy to detangle, this lightweight conditioner is gentle enough for daily use as it works to improve the overall health of the hair; nourishing and strengthening it. Vegan-friendly and formulated without gluten, parabens and mineral oils, this daily conditioner is best used in conjunction with 360 Daily Shampoo.<br/></p>', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul class=\"dual-column\"><li>Althaea Root Extract</li><li>Calendula Flower Extract</li><li>Chamomile Extract</li><li>Mallow Leaf Extract</li></ul><div class=\"inline-text-area | xsmall-text\"><h3>Full ingredients</h3>                        Aqua (Water), Myristyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Cetrimonium Chloride, Hydrogenated Olive Oil Stearyl Esters, Melissa Officinalis Flower/Leaf/Stem Extract (Melissa Officinalis Leaf Extract), Chamomilla Recutita Extract (Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Extract), Parfum (Fragrance), Althaea Officinalis Root Extract, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract, Malva Sylvestris Leaf Extract (Malva Sylvestris (Mallow) Leaf Extract), Polyquaternium-7, Bis (C13-15 Alkoxy) Pg Amodimethicone, Propylene Glycol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil (Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil), Lactic Acid, Tetrasodium Edta, Imidazolidinyl Urea, Methylchloroisothiazolinone, Methylisothiazolinone                    </div></div>', '<d