(61, 'feather-touch-1+1-deal', 'Feather Touch 1+1 Deal', 'Buy 1 Fusion Featherjet Plus Professional Hair Dryer and get 1 free Fusion Slick Touch Original Iron. Receive a bonus value of $102 with the Feather Touch 1+1 Deal.', '<p>Fusion Feather Touch 1+1 Deal includes:</p><ul><li>1 x <a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/tools-brushes/electrical/hair-dryers/fusion-featherjet-plus-professional-hair-dryer-in-black-05956/\">Fusion Featherjet Plus Professional Hair</a><a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/tools-brushes/electrical/hair-dryers/fusion-featherjet-plus-professional-hair-dryer-in-black-05956/\"></a></li><li>1 x FREE Fusion Slick Touch Original Iron</li><li>Bonus value of $102</li></ul>', '', '', '05944_thumbnail_7.png', 13, 14, 4, '05944', 36, 45, 2.83907, 23, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(62, 'slicktouch-wide-straightening-iron', 'SlickTouch Wide Straightening Iron', 'With fast heat up time and ceramic floating plates, discover the ultimate experience in salon hair styling with the SlickTouch Wide Straightening Iron by Fusion.', '<ul><li>2 inch Nano Ceramic Floating Plates</li><li>Wide plate design for thicker, longer hair</li><li>Quick heat recovery in less than 2 seconds for continuous use</li><li>Analogue temperature control - fast heat up to 150-230° in 30 seconds</li><li>Worldwide dual voltage </li><li>360° tangle free swivel cord</li><li>Automatically switches off when not in use after 60 minutes</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $219.00.</p><p>The Fusion SlickTouch Wide Iron is the next step in elevating your hair styling game. This professional hair straightener features nano ceramic floating plates with a 2 inch wide design suitable for thicker, longer hair. Negative ions smooth and tighten the hair\'s outer cuticle layer to make it more manageable, feel softer and look shinier. This means SlickTouch reconditions and restructures the hair to give it greater control and enhanced smoothness every time you use it. Ceramic technology seals in moisture, natural oils and hair colour for complete protection. Quick heat in less than 2 seconds ensures maintenance of heat for continuous use, and a heat up time of 30 seconds to 150-230° is perfect for salon results. This hair iron automatically switches off after 60 minutes of idleness, and features a 360° swivel cord to help avoid cord tangles and make it easier to access hard to reach sections. Worldwide dual voltage provides usage in all countries, catering to any traveller\'s needs.  With Fusion SlickTouch, salon professionals can experience a truly versatile multi-styler that\'s great for straightening and smoothing hair, spiral curling and creating flicks and waves.<br/></p>', '', '', '05933_thumbnail_3.png', 13, 14, 4, '05933', 47, 68, 2.3341, 10, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(63, 'slicktouch-standard-straightening-iron', 'SlickTouch Standard Straightening Iron', 'With fast heat up time and ceramic floating plates, discover the ultimate experience in salon hair styling with the SlickTouch Standard Straightening Iron by Fusion.', '<ul><li>1 inch Nano Ceramic Floating Plates</li><li>Quick heat recovery in less than 2 seconds for continuous use</li><li>Analogue temperature control - fast heat up to 150-230° in 30 seconds</li><li>Worldwide dual voltage </li><li>360° tangle free swivel cord</li><li>Automatically switches off when not in use after 60 minutes</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $219.00.</p><p>The Fusion SlickTouch Standard Iron is the next step in elevating your hair styling game. This professional hair straightener features nano ceramic floating plates to ensure perfect contact with hair. Negative ions smooth and tighten the hair\'s outer cuticle layer to make it more manageable, feel softer and look shinier. This means SlickTouch reconditions and restructures the hair to give it greater control and enhanced smoothness every time you use it. Ceramic technology seals in moisture, natural oils and hair colour for complete protection. Quick heat in less than 2 seconds ensures maintenance of heat for continuous use, and with a heat up time of 30 seconds to 150-230° is perfect for salon results. This hair iron automatically switches off after 60 minutes of idleness, and features a 360° swivel cord to help avoid cord tangles and make it easier to access hard to reach sections. Worldwide dual voltage provides usage in all countries, catering to any traveller\'s needs.  With Fusion SlickTouch, salon professionals can experience a truly versatile multi-styler that\'s great for straightening and smoothing hair, spiral curling and creating flicks and waves.<br/></p>', '', '', '05932_thumbnail_4.png', 13, 14, 1, '05932', 22, 37, 2.52078, 10, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(64, 'original-iron', 'Original Iron', 'The Alchemy Original Iron features innovative, market-leading technology for completely personalised hair styling, and comes with a rose gold styling case for easy storage. Achieve exceptional results that are kind on hair with CLOUD NINE.', '<ul><li>7 temperature control options suiting every hair type; from 100-200°C</li><li>Heat up time of 20 seconds</li><li>Mineral-infused ceramic plates achieve exceptional results at a lower temperature</li><li>Floating plate design cushions the impact on hair, minimising drag and breakage</li><li>Hibernation Mode automatically cools the Iron when not used for 30 minutes</li><li>Swivel cord for easy usage</li><li>Universal voltage, identification chip and a 12 month warranty for peace of mind</li><li>Comes with a rose gold styling case</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $340.00.</p><p>Offering the ultimate experience in heat-styling, the CLOUD NINE Alchemy Original Iron is guaranteed to deliver sleek, luxurious and long-lasting results. The Original Iron features 7 temperature controls from 100-200°C, allowing all hair types the opportunity to smooth, curl, wave or straighten at lower temperatures. Its mineral-infused ceramic plates are designed to lock in moisture, seal the cuticle and minimise damage to the hair\'s natural structure. With a heat up time of 20 seconds, a patented MiCOM technology adjusts the temperature according to thermal sensor calculations, ensuring an even and smooth distribution of heat across the ceramic surface. These plates feature a floating design that cushions the impact on each section of the hair, minimising drag, pinches and breakage. This hair iron features a Hibernation Mode that automatically cools the straightener when not used for 30 minutes. A swivel cord and protective heat guard add extra comfort and usability to the iron, while universal voltage, an identification chip and a 12 month warranty offer peace of mind. Based on CLOUD NINE\'S ethos of kinder styling, the Original Iron has revolutionised the heat-styling world, offering limitless styling flexibility with a glossy, healthy finish.<br/></p>', '', '', '79000_thumbnail_8.png', 13, 15, 2, '79000', 27, 48, 4.03972, 8, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(65, 'keratin-230-25mm-ceramic-straightener', 'Keratin 230 25mm Ceramic Straightener', 'With ultra-smooth floating plates, the Silver Bullet Keratin 230°C 25mm Ceramic Straightener leaves hair feeling silky and smooth for longer.', '<ul><li>Ceramic/Tourmaline floating plates</li><li>Adjustable heat dial: 80-230°C</li><li>Cool to touch tips</li><li>360° swivel cord</li><li>25mm plate design</li><li>Dual voltage for universal usage</li><li>Comes with a heat pouch, crocodile clips, styling comb and paddle brush</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $259.95.</p><p>Using Keratin, the Silver Bullet 25mm Ceramic Straightener leaves hair feeling smooth, shiny and strong. Straighten, curl and create without frizzing or snagging hair. <br/></p>', '', '', '76230_thumbnail_6.png', 13, 11, 1, '76230', 41, 50, 4.7086, 49, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(66, 'fastlane-clipless-ceramic-curling-wand-32mm', 'Fastlane Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand 32mm', 'Create textured curls and waves with the Fastlane Ceramic Oval Conical Curler from Silver Bullet.', '<ul><li>Ceramic Oval Curler</li><li>Instant heat-up</li><li>Safety cool-tip end protects fingers</li><li>Easy grip, heat resistant handle</li><li>Clipless design</li><li>Dual voltage for universal usage</li><li>Comes with heat protective mat </li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $148.95.</p><p>With a faster heat up function and innovative oval shaped Ceramic Wand, the Silver Bullet Fastlane Conical Curler produces loose waves with volume and texture. With its clipless design, create free-form waves and curls with ease.<br/></p>', '', '', '76350_thumbnail_5.png', 14, 11, 2, '76350', 20, 36, 1.63418, 29, 100, '2022-02-02');
