(67, 'fastlane-clipless-ceramic-curling-wand-25mm', 'Fastlane Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand 25mm', 'For smooth, long lasting curls use the Silver Bullet Fastlane Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand 25mm.', '<ul><li>25mm Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand</li><li>Longer barrel length for better hair coverage</li><li>Adjustable heat settings up to 230</li><li>LCD temperature display</li><li>Cool-touch tip prevents fingers from burning</li><li>Dual voltage for universal usage</li><li>Comes with a heat resistant glove</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $102.00.</p><p>Create stunning curls with the Silver Bullet Fastlane Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand 25mm. With speedy heat-up ability, this clip-free styling wand creates smooth and bouncy waves with ease.<br/></p>', '', '', '76340_thumbnail_5.png', 14, 11, 4, '76340', 26, 32, 3.53778, 11, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(68, 'fastlane-clipless-ceramic-curling-wand-32mm', 'Fastlane Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand 32mm', 'For smooth, long lasting curls use the Silver Bullet Fastlane Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand 32mm.', '<ul><li>32mm Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand</li><li>Longer barrel length for better hair coverage</li><li>Adjustable heat settings up to 230</li><li>LCD temperature display</li><li>Cool-touch tip prevents fingers from burning</li><li>Dual voltage for universal usage</li><li>Comes with a heat resistant glove</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $102.00.</p><p>Create stunning curls with the Silver Bullet Fastlane Clipless Ceramic Curling Wand 32mm. With speedy heat-up ability, this clip-free styling wand creates smooth and bouncy waves with ease.<br/></p>', '', '', '76342_thumbnail_5.png', 14, 11, 2, '76342', 35, 56, 4.69695, 11, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(69, 'curling-wand', 'Curling Wand', 'The versatile Alchemy Curling Wand is the ultimate tool for effortless curls and volume, and comes with a rose gold styling case for easy storage. Achieve exceptional results that are kind on the hair with CLOUD NINE.', '<ul><li>The ultimate tool for effortless curls, waves and volume; especially in long or thick hair</li><li>One-touch temperature control from high, medium to low heat</li><li>Clear LED display for constant temperature visibility</li><li>25mm mineral-infused, slow-baked, ceramic coated barrel polishes and shines</li><li>Hibernation Mode automatically cools the wand after 30 minutes when not in use</li><li>Convenient swivel cord and kick stand</li><li>Universal voltage, identification chip and a 12 month warranty for peace of mind</li><li>Comes with a rose gold styling case</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $245.00.</p><p>Offering complete styling versatility, the CLOUD NINE Alchemy Curling Wand is the ultimate tool for effortless curls, beachy waves, adding texture and creating volume; especially in long or thick hair. This curling wand features a 25mm, mineral-infused, slow-baked coated barrel that polishes and glosses hair giving it a natural, smooth shine. A temperature control switches from low to medium to high, allowing complete personalisation and care based on the condition and texture of the hair. With a clear LED display, the chosen temperature will always be visible, giving every user complete control. This curling wand features a Hibernation Mode, which turns off after 30 minutes when not in use. A swivel cord, kick stand and protective glove add extra comfort and usability to the wand, while universal voltage, an identification chip and a 12 month warranty offer peace of mind. Crafted from CLOUD NINE\'S ethos of kinder styling, the Curling Wand offers infinite styling flexibility for voluminous hair with a glossy, healthy finish.<br/></p>', '', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ol><li>Always wear the protective glove provided on the hand used to wind hair around the wand barrel.</li><li>Plug into the mains power and turn on by pressing and holding the power button down for two seconds. The auto light will turn blue and the MED light will flash red. The MED light will remain green once the MED temperature is reached. To select the LOW or HIGH temperatures, press the power switch again until the selected temperature flashes red. The indicator will turn green once the selected temperature is reached. Begin styling.</li><li>Always use the wand on clean, dry hair.</li><li>Should a higher or lower temperature be required during styling, press the power button again until the selected temperature flashes red. The indicator will turn green once the temperature is reached. This allows time for the wand to cool down or heat up sufficiently.</li><li>When the wand is in AUTO mode, it will automatically heat to the MED setting when switched on. To change the AUTO mode to manual, hold down the AUTO button for two seconds, whilst the wand is switched on. The blue AUTO light will turn off. The wand is now in manual mode and will start on the last used temperature setting when turned on.</li><li>To return the wand to AUTO mode, hold down the AUTO button whilst the wand is switched on. The AUTO light will remain blue.</li><li>Once finished, turn the power off by pressing the power button for two seconds until the green indicator light has gone off and unplug from the mains power supply.</li></ol>NOTE: Never wrap the cord around the wand. The wand also has a kick stand integrated into the back of the handle. To use the stand, lift the stand with the tip of a finger and extend out towards the barrel. Place on a flat surface. Replace the stand into the handle before styling.                </div>', '79032_thumbnail_8.png', 14, 15, 4, '79032', 48, 61, 1.58344, 29, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(70, 'professional-curling-wand', 'Professional Curling Wand', 'The Sericite Professional Curling Wand is the ultimate tool for effortless, infinite curls and volume; especially in long or thick hair. Achieve exceptional, long-lasting results that are kind on the hair with CLOUD NINE.', '<ul><li>The ultimate tool for effortless curls, waves and volume; especially in long or thick hair</li><li>One-touch temperature control from high, medium to low heat</li><li>Clear LED display for constant temperature visibility</li><li>25mm mineral-infused, slow-baked, ceramic coated barrel polishes and shines</li><li>Hibernation Mode automatically cools the Wand when inactive for 30 minutes</li><li>Convenient swivel cord and kick stand</li><li>Universal voltage, identification chip and a 12 month warranty for peace of mind</li><li>Designed for professional use</li></ul><p>Offering complete styling versatility, the CLOUD NINE Sericite Professional Curling Wand is the ultimate tool for effortless curls, beachy waves, adding texture and creating volume; especially in long or thick hair. This professional curling wand features a 25mm, mineral-infused, slow-baked coated barrel that polishes and glosses hair giving it a natural, smooth shine. A temperature control switches from low to medium to high, allowing complete personalisation and care based on the condition and texture of the hair. With a clear LED display, the chosen temperature will always be visible, giving every user complete control. This styling wand features a Hibernation Mode, which automatically cools after 30 minutes when not in use. A swivel cord, kick stand and protective glove add extra comfort and usability to the wand, while universal voltage, an identification chip and a 12 month warranty offer peace of mind. Crafted from CLOUD NINE\'S ethos of kinder styling, the Curling Wand offers incredible styling flexibility for voluminous hair with a glossy, healthy finish.<br/></p>', '', '', '79134_thumbnail_6.png', 14, 16, 3, '79134', 45, 63, 0.919815, 11, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(71, 'power-dry-2000w-hair-dryer-in-black', 'Power Dry 2000W Hair Dryer in Black', 'Featuring a professional and powerful 2000W AC motor and Tourmaline Ionic Technology, this hairdryer is suitable for everyday salon use. Achieve a healthier, smoother & shinier finish with the Wahl Power Dry 2000W Dryer in Black.', '<ul><li>Powerful 2000W AC Motor</li><li>Tourmaline Ionic Technology that reduces static &amp; keeps moisture in the hair cuticles, resulting in a healthier, smoother &amp; shinier finish</li><li>Includes 2 concentrator nozzles, one slim and one wide</li><li>Choice of 3 heat and 2 speed settings plus a cold shot button to lock in style</li><li>Lightweight with an ergonomic handle for balance and control</li><li>Low noise and a removable filter for easy cleaning</li><li>3m cable and hanging loop for easy use and storage</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $89.95.</p>                Wahl Power Dry 2000W Dryer in Black features a powerful 2000W AC motor with a lightweight and ergonomic handle, helping to achieve balance and control when blow-drying. With Tourmaline Ionic Technology that reduces static and keeps moisture in the hair cuticle, this dryer achieves a healthier, smoother, and shinier finish. There are 2 concentrator nozzles available, one slim for direct heat and one wider for greater airflow. An additional 3 heat and 2 speed settings allows for a more customised experience. A cold shot button is also featured to lock in style, along with a removable filter for easy cleaning. The 3m long cable allows for seamless navigation around the workspace and can be easily stored using the hanging loop. The Wahl Power Dry Dryer has been carefully created to achieve outstanding results for everyday salon use.', '', '', '05400_thumbnail_3.png', 15, 17, 4, '05400', 43, 58, 1.49276, 16, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(72, 'feather-touch-1+1-deal', 'Feather Touch 1+1 Deal', 'Buy 1 Fusion Featherjet Plus Professional Hair Dryer and get 1 free Fusion Slick Touch Original Iron. Receive a bonus value of $102 with the Feather Touch 1+1 Deal.', '<p>Fusion Feather Touch 1+1 Deal includes:</p><ul><li>1 x <a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/tools-brushes/electrical/hair-dryers/fusion-featherjet-plus-professional-hair-dryer-in-black-05956/\">Fusion Featherjet Plus Professional Hair</a><a href=\"https://www.thehaircaregroup.com/tools-brushes/electrical/hair-dryers/fusion-featherjet-plus-professional-hair-dryer-in-black-05956/\"></a></li><li>1 x FREE Fusion Slick Touch Original Iron</li><li>Bonus value of $102</li></ul>', '', '', '05944_thumbnail_7.png', 15, 14, 2, '05944', 48, 61, 2.3523, 1, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(73, 'universal-small-mesh-diffuser', 'Universal Small Mesh Diffuser', 'YS Park Universal Small Mesh Diffuser fits onto any hair dryer, and is lightweight and compact to fit perfectly in your kit bag. Use the small size to concentrate heat on a smaller area.', '<ul><li>Universal small mesh diffuser with an adjustable strap fits onto any hair dryer</li><li>Small size allows more air through to concentrate heat over a smaller area</li><li>Compact design is easy to fold and transport</li><li>Retains the natural moisture of hair when drying</li><li>Made with silver and titanium particles</li><li>90mm W x 120mm L x 40-90mm neck width</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $51.00.</p>', '', '', '54104_thumbnail_2.png', 15, 18, 2, '54104', 15, 35, 0.539813, 13, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(74, 'universal-large-mesh-diffuser', 'Universal Large Mesh Diffuser', 'YS Park Universal Large Mesh Diffuser fits onto any hair dryer, and is lightweight and compact to fit perfectly in your kit bag. Use the large size to spread heat over a larger area.', '<ul><li>Universal large mesh diffuser with an adjustable strap fits onto any hair dryer</li><li>Large size is more delicate and spreads heat over a larger area</li><li>Compact design is easy to fold and transport</li><li>Retains the natural moisture of hair when drying</li><li>Made with silver and titanium particles</li><li>140mm W x 160mm L x 50-100mm neck width</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $61.00.</p>', '', '', '54100_thumbnail_3.png', 15, 18, 3, '54100', 26, 32, 2.92865, 9, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(75, 'alto-end-cap-&-filter', 'Alto End Cap & Filter', 'Add this Fusion Alto End Cap/Filter as a replacement or spare part for the Fusion Alto Hair Dryer.', '<ul><li>Replacement End Cap/Filter for Fusion Alto Dryer</li><li>For professional salon use</li></ul><div><br/></div>', '', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\"><ul><li>Follow instructed product directions and safety precautions </li></ul></div>', '06010_thumbnail_0.png', 15, 14, 2, '06010', 24, 40, 3.21837, 11, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(76, 'corn-cutter-blades-10pk', 'Corn Cutter Blades 10pk', 'Durable and ready to use, add the Corn Cutter Blade Pack to your professional pedicure kit.', '<ul><li>Replacement blades</li><li>To be used with Corn Plane tool</li><li>Ready to use </li><li>10 Pack</li></ul>', '', '', '77213_thumbnail_1.png', 16, 19, 2, '77213', 12, 25, 4.72391, 34, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(77, 'blade-care-plus-spray', 'Blade Care Plus Spray', 'Get a 7-in-1 blade care experience with the Andis Blade Care Plus Spray.', '<ul><li>7 actions in one!</li><li>Works as a blade coolant, deodoriser, lubricant and cleaner</li><li>Prevents blades from rusting </li><li>Formulated with Vitamin E</li><li>De-contaminant - safe for use by humans and animals </li><li>Increases efficiency and performance of professional blades </li></ul><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $40.95.</p>', '', '', '03447_thumbnail_1.png', 16, 20, 1, '03447', 10, 16, 4.9817, 26, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(78, 't-outliner-cordless-li-stainless-steel-replacement-blade', 'T-Outliner Cordless LI Stainless Steel Replacement Blade', 'A stainless steel replacement blade crafted for use with the Andis T-Outliner Cordless Trimmer. Experience a close-cutting, T-blade design with the T-Outliner Cordless LI Stainless Steel Replacement Blade by Andis.', '<ul><li>Polished, stainless steel replacement T-blade</li><li>Stays sharp while resisting corrosion and rust</li><li>Comfort Edge blade cuts close and can be adjusted to zero overlap</li><li>Suitable for use with the Andis T-Outliner Cordless Trimmer</li><li>Made in the USA</li></ul><p class=\"product-detail__rrp\">The recommended retail price (RRP) for this item is $95.95.</p>                The Andis T-Outliner Cordless LI Stainless Steel Replacement Blade features a perfectly polished, T-blade design; ideal for incredibly close cutting and outlining. This replacement blade stays sharp while resisting corrosion and rust, offering long-term performance. Its Comfort Edge Technology can be adjusted to zero overlap for the smoothest finish. Made in the USA, this trimmer blade is suitable for use with the Andis T-Outliner Cordless Trimmer.', '', '', '03444_thumbnail_0.png', 16, 20, 3, '03444', 39, 50, 3.80786, 11, 0, '2022-02-02'),
(79, 'astra-double-edge-platinum-razor-blades-pack-of-5', 'Astra Double Edge Platinum Razor Blades Pack of 5', 'Astra Platinum Double Edged Barber Razor Blades 5 Pack are a pro-choice for traditional men\'s grooming and Barbering.', '<ul><li>5 Pack Razor Blades</li><li>Double edged</li><li>For professional Barber use </li></ul><p>Use premium Astra Platinum Double Edged Razor Blades for traditional men\'s shaving. Ideal for professional use, these replaceable blades come in a handy 5 pack. <br/></p>', '', '', '05356_thumbnail_1.png', 16, 21, 2, '05356', 18, 32, 3.38053, 1, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(80, 'astra-platinum-double-edge-razor-blades-box-100', 'Astra Platinum Double Edge Razor Blades Box 100', 'Astra Platinum Double Edged Razor Blades Box of 100 are a pro-choice for traditional men\'s grooming and Barbering.', '<ul><li>100 replaceable Razor Blades</li><li>Double edged</li><li>For professional Barber use </li></ul><p>Use premium Astra Platinum Double Edged Razor Blades for traditional men\'s shaving. Ideal for professional use, these replaceable blades come in a 20 x 5 pack for salon convenience. <br/></p>', '', '', '05357_thumbnail_1.png', 16, 21, 1, '05357', 30, 48, 0.336987, 48, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(81, '7-jelly-barbering-scissors', '7 Jelly Barbering Scissors', 'Handcrafted from Japanese steel, the Washi Jelly 7\" Barbering Scissors are a pro choice for precision cutting and styling.', '<ul><li>For professional use only</li><li>Made from Hitachi Japanese Steel</li><li>Barbering Scissors</li><li>7-inch blades</li><li>Includes protective case, cloth and oil</li></ul><p>The Washi Jelly 7\" Barbering Scissors are designed for comfort, performance and longevity. Made from authentic Hitachi Japanese Steel, these barber shears come with a Washi lifetime guarantee. The choice tool for hair professionals globally for over 30 years, each pair of Scissors are packaged with its own protective case, cleaning cloth and scissor oil.<br/></p>', '', '', '75512_thumbnail_3.png', 17, 22, 2, '75512', 39, 53, 1.80817, 48, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(82, '6-jelly-barbering-scissors', '6 Jelly Barbering Scissors', 'Handcrafted from Japanese steel, the Washi Jelly 6\" Barbering Scissors are a pro choice for precision cutting and styling.', '<ul><li>For professional use only</li><li>Made from Hitachi Japanese Steel</li><li>Barbering Scissors</li><li>6-inch blades</li><li>Includes protective case, cloth and oil</li></ul><p>The Washi Jelly 6\" Barbering Scissors are designed for comfort, performance and longevity. Made from authentic Hitachi Japanese Steel, these barber shears come with a Washi lifetime guarantee. The choice tool for hair professionals globally for over 30 years, each pair of Scissors are packaged with its own protective case, cleaning cloth and scissor oil.<br/></p>', '', '', '75508_thumbnail_3.png', 17, 22, 3, '75508', 25, 40, 4.92383, 13, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(83, '6.5-jelly-barbering-scissors', '6.5 Jelly Barbering Scissors', 'Handcrafted from Japanese steel, the Washi Jelly 6.5\" Barbering Scissors are a pro choice for precision cutting and styling.', '<ul><li>For professional use only</li><li>Made from Hitachi Japanese Steel</li><li>Barbering Scissors</li><li>6.5-inch blades</li><li>Includes protective case, cloth and oil</li></ul><p>The Washi Jelly 6.5\" Barbering Scissors are designed for comfort, performance and longevity. Made from authentic Hitachi Japanese Steel, these thinning shears come with a Washi lifetime guarantee. The choice tool for hair professionals globally for over 30 years, each pair of Scissors are packaged with its own protective case, cleaning cloth and scissor oil.<br/></p>', '', '', '75510_thumbnail_3.png', 17, 22, 1, '75510', 49, 54, 3.09205, 44, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(84, 'left-handed-5.5-stainless-steel-double-tang-thinner-shears', 'Left Handed 5.5 Stainless Steel Double Tang Thinner Shears', 'Made from durable Stainless Steel, the Sonic Series Stainless Steel Left Handed Thinner Double Tang 5.5\" Shears are a pro choice for premium cutting and styling.', '<ul><li>Left Handed Thinning Scissors</li><li>Made from Stainless Steel</li><li>Double Tang</li><li>5.5-inch</li></ul><p>The Left Handed Sonic Series Double Tang 5.5\" Thinning Scissors are designed for comfort, performance and longevity. Made from Stainless Steel, these shears enable stylists of all levels to cut with precision and control.<br/></p>', '', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\">                    Caring for your scissors: <ul><li>For optimum performance clean with scissor oil and cloth regularly.</li><li>When not in use store back into pouch.</li><li>Defer to a professional sharpening expert to sharpen blades.</li></ul></div>', '75607_thumbnail_3.png', 17, 23, 2, '75607', 21, 27, 2.55598, 9, 100, '2022-02-02'),
(85, 'stainless-steel-thinner-double-tang-5.5', 'Stainless Steel Thinner Double Tang 5.5', 'Made from durable Stainless Steel, the Sonic Series 5.5\" Thinner Shears with Double Tang are a pro choice for premium cutting and styling.', '<ul><li>5.5-inch Thinning Scissors</li><li>Made from Stainless Steel</li><li>Double Tang</li><li>Includes protective case, cloth and oil</li></ul><div><br/></div><p>The Sonic Series Double Tang 5.5\" Thinning Scissors are designed for comfort, performance and longevity. Made from Stainless Steel, these thinning shears come with its own case and care kit, helping maintain the scissors high performance and quality. <br/></p>', '', '<div class=\"wysiwyg-compact has-grey-markers\">                    Caring for your scissors: For optimum performance clean with scissor oil and cloth regularly.When not in use store back into pouch.Defer to a professional sharpening expert to sharpen blades.                </div>', '75606_thumbnail_4.png', 17, 23, 3, '75606', 27, 42, 3.61007, 25, 100, '2022-02-02');
